    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Oxford Orthopaedic Questionnaire - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_oxford_orthopaedic_questionnaire">Oxford Orthopaedic Questionnaire</xref>
 is an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_assessment_tool">ASSESSMENT TOOL</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_oxford_orthopaedic_questionnaire">Oxford Orthopaedic Questionnaire</xref>
 is a 12 item questionnaire to measure outcomes before and after:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_primary_hip_replacement_surgery">Primary Hip Replacement Surgery</xref>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_revision_hip_replacement_surgery">Revision Hip Replacement Surgery</xref>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_primary_knee_replacement_surgery">Primary Knee Replacement Surgery</xref>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_revision_knee_replacement_surgery">Revision Knee Replacement Surgery</xref>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_primary_shoulder_replacement_surgery">Primary Shoulder Replacement Surgery</xref>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_revision_shoulder_replacement_surgery">Revision Shoulder Replacement Surgery</xref>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>treatment for shoulder instability problems.</p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
For further information on the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_oxford_orthopaedic_questionnaire">Oxford Orthopaedic Questionnaires</xref>, see the 
              <xref href="http://phi.uhce.ox.ac.uk/ox_scores.php"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Patient-Reported Outcomes Measurement Group website</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
